                "name": "Acidic Gore",
                "ability_type": "Supernatural",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su",
                "text": "The Emperor of Scales\u2019 giant severed head continually drips blood and gore that burn like acid. Any creature within 10 feet of the Emperor of Scales must make a DC 25 Reflex save or be sprayed by droplets of acidic blood, taking 2d6 points of acid damage. The save DC is Constitution-based."
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "name": "Command Snakes",
                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex",
                "text": "As a free action, the Emperor of Scales can command any snake or serpent with the animal or magical beast type, as the <i>dominate animal</i> spell. The target can resist the command with a DC 25 Will save."
